{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, one day, I met [NON-ENGLISH] on the street again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she comes to me and tells me a story, that she heard that one of the-- there were those Polish employment office, employee part of the German employment office.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That if you, for a bribe, one of them, whatever his name was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He may send you to Germany as a slave laborer on false papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you may survive this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told her, look, I don't have any money to pay anybody anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even know what I-- what I really-- I wish sometimes I would remember what I wore, how filthy I was, eaten up by lice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she says, if I find the Jewish policeman who will go-- because he cannot get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean everything is punishable by death, especially at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would you go with me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe two, three days later, she got hold of a Jewish fellow she knew as a policeman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he walks out with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he goes with us to this fellow's address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this fellow's not even home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we walk back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, again, you know, that's what I consider so strange, those little things that sound as if somebody would-- you couldn't even-- I don't think I could dream it up, because I didn't have such a fantasy.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we're walking-- you know, we're walking back to the ghetto, and we pass another street on the way to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this policeman, we pass her by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the policeman says, here lives another Polish employee of the employment office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once you are out, maybe you want to ask him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] rings a bell.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
